1. Prerequesites

To build FileZilla Server you'll need the following:

- libfilezilla 0.9.0 or greater
- Visual Studio 2015
- OpenSSL
- Zlib

2. Preparation

- Compile libfilezilla, Zlib and OpenSSL, see their respective documentation for instructions
- Copy source\Dependencies.props.example to source\Dependencies.props
- Open source\Dependencies.props in a text editor and change the paths in it

3. Building FileZilla

- Open "source\FileZilla Server.sln" in Visual Studio and hit F5.